Class OutOfResourceException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.iresource_source.exceptions.OutOfResourceException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class OutOfResourceException
extends Exception
    Exception thrown by methods of implementations of IResourceSource when client tries to access resource that is not available but will become available later (the client may use IResourceSource.onAvailable(IPoorAction) to wait for resource).
